<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nod-v">nod <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /nɒd/    美 /nɑːd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt [表示同意或打招呼等] 点头：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I asked him if he would help me and he nodded.
我问他能否帮帮我，他点了点头。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mother <strong>nodded (her) approval</strong>.
我妈妈点头表示赞同。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was phoning someone, so I <strong>nodded to / at</strong> her and went away.
她正在给人打电话，所以我向她点头示意后就离开了。</p><footer>2014 四川改</footer></div></div>